    "en": {
      "title": "China has provided 1000 metric tons of rice to Sri Lanka in the 2nd phase",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "China has provided 1,000 metric tons of rice to Sri Lanka in the second phase for the school nutrition program.",
        "China has said that it will provide 10,000 metric tons of rice for the school lunch program to Sri Lanka, which is caught in a severe economic crisis.",
        "On June 28, China had provided one thousand metric tons of rice to Sri Lanka, but now it has provided one thousand metric tons of rice."
      ],
